column5: There used to be a place in Fort Frances called the Red Dog Inn, will be needing a place to stay at the end of July, can anybody tell me if this place is still open? Used to love their hot wings special but was looking for the place on the net and cannot find it listed under motels... Please let me know
I got this number off of a Google search..not sure how old the page was though...807-274-7721 Right next door is a Super 8 and if youre heading west theres the Emo Inn
